        "column_WYUpRY": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Argent.jpg",
            "title": "Argent",
            "text": "<p>Argent offers a premium selection of <strong>toilets</strong> that combine sleek European design with everyday functionality. As the exclusive Australian distributor of leading international bathroom brands like <strong>Villeroy & Boch</strong> and <strong>Bette</strong>, Argent delivers quality, innovation, and water efficiency across its toilet range. Designed to suit modern Australian homes and commercial projects alike, Argent toilets balance aesthetics with long-lasting performance.</p>",
            "link_label": "Argent Toilets",
            "link": "shopify://collections/argent-toilets"
          }
        },
        "column_7peE9M": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Feature-Brands_Caroma_13fec2f7-afe1-45fe-b34c-0663f878a211.png",
            "title": "Caroma",
            "text": "<p>Caroma is an iconic Australian brand known for pioneering water-saving toilet technology without compromising on style or comfort. Their range of toilets is designed for modern Australian homes, with options that include rimless bowls, soft-close seats, and superior flushing performance. Backed by decades of innovation and local expertise, Caroma toilets deliver durability, efficiency, and timeless design for every bathroom.</p>",
            "link_label": "Caroma Toilets",
            "link": "shopify://collections/caroma-toilets"
          }
        },
        "column_h3caVL": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/fienza-logo.png",
            "title": "Fienza",
            "text": "<p>Fienza combines modern aesthetics with practical design across its range of toilets, offering stylish solutions for Australian bathrooms. With a focus on clean lines, comfort, and efficient flushing, Fienza toilets are crafted to suit both contemporary and classic interiors. The brand is known for its attention to detail, quality finishes, and options that include rimless designs, soft-close seats, and space-saving configurations—making Fienza a reliable choice for residential and commercial projects.</p>",
            "link_label": "Fienza Toilets",
            "link": "shopify://collections/fienza-toilets"
          }
        },
        "column_AKMnGW": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/SEIMA_LOGO_Black_327e24c1-eab7-4410-802c-a0c0b35441e9.png",
            "title": "Seima",
            "text": "<p>Seima offers a refined collection of toilets that blend minimalist Australian design with advanced performance. Known for its commitment to form and function, Seima toilets feature rimless bowls, hygienic glazing, and soft-close seats to enhance comfort and cleanliness. With options in wall-faced, back-to-wall, and in-wall concealed configurations, Seima delivers versatile toilet solutions that suit both contemporary and classic bathroom spaces.</p>",
            "link_label": "Seima Toilets",
            "link": "shopify://collections/seima-toilets"
          }
        },
        "column_L4wHB8": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/StGeorge_Logo_7b3fc39c-c64e-4f09-92d2-74117131b31f.png",
            "title": "St George",
            "text": "<p>St George delivers advanced bathroom technology through its Concord Smart Toilet range, blending modern design with intelligent features. The Concord model offers rear and female cleansing functions, adjustable seat temperature, a warm air dryer, UV nozzle disinfection, and an automatic lid. With a WELS 4-star rating and an average flush of 3.4L, it ensures water efficiency without compromising performance. The toilet also includes a soft nightlight and premium remote control for enhanced user convenience. </p>",
            "link_label": "St George Toilets",
            "link": "shopify://collections/st-george"
          }
        },
        "column_maJQGd": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Brand_Logo_VilleroyandBoch_b7e128fb-ccf8-46ba-a7c2-540a792794bc.jpg",
            "title": "Villeroy & Boch",
            "text": "<p>Established in 1748, Villeroy & Boch is a renowned European brand celebrated for its exceptional craftsmanship and innovative bathroom solutions. Their toilet collections, including popular ranges like Subway, Architectura, and O.novo, seamlessly blend timeless design with modern functionality. Features such as rimless DirectFlush technology, soft-close seats, and water-efficient systems ensure both hygiene and comfort. Whether you’re seeking wall-hung, back-to-wall, or floor-standing models, Villeroy & Boch offers a diverse selection to complement any bathroom aesthetic.</p>",
            "link_label": "Villeroy & Boch Toilets",
            "link": "shopify://collections/villeroy-boch-toilets"
          }
        }
      },
