    "image_with_text_HEmJMW": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_Jkt4NN": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Wall Hung Toilets",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_GFWUpd": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Wall hung toilets — sometimes referred to as floating toilets — are a premium choice for contemporary and architecturally-designed bathrooms. With the toilet pan mounted directly to the wall and the cistern hidden behind a wall cavity or within cabinetry, these models create the illusion of a more spacious bathroom by exposing the floor underneath.</p><p>This design not only looks sleek and modern but also allows for easy floor cleaning and reduces contact points — a benefit for hygiene-conscious homeowners. The installation requires a sturdy in-wall frame and proper wall reinforcement, making wall hung toilets better suited to new builds or major renovations.</p><p>Their minimalist aesthetic can be further enhanced with flush plates in brushed metal or matte black finishes, and many models feature rimless bowls and advanced flushing systems for greater hygiene. With options from brands like Geberit and Villeroy & Boch, wall hung toilets bring a refined, designer touch to premium bathroom spaces.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_Ga6L8m": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "Shop Wall Hung Toilets",
            "button_link": "shopify://collections/wall-hung-toilets"
          }
        }
