    "image_with_text_9dBPy7": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_7nb9pW": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Smart Toilets",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_APqfWz": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Smart toilets represent the next evolution in bathroom comfort and hygiene. These advanced models incorporate intelligent technology that automates and enhances everyday use, transforming the toilet into a wellness experience.</p><p>Key features typically include:</p><ul><li><strong>Integrated bidet</strong> with adjustable water pressure and temperature<br/></li><li><strong>Heated seats </strong>for comfort, especially during colder months<br/></li><li><strong>Warm air drying</strong> and UV sterilisation for superior cleanliness<br/></li><li><strong>Motion-activated lids</strong>, automatic flushing, and soft-close systems<br/></li><li><strong>Nights lights </strong>for low-light use<br/></li><li><strong>Remote controls </strong>or wall-mounted panels for customisation<br/></li></ul><p>Smart toilets are perfect for modern households that value convenience, luxury, and accessibility. They’re especially beneficial for multigenerational homes, people with limited mobility, and anyone seeking a more hygienic alternative to traditional toilet paper.</p><p>Brands like St George are leading the way in affordable luxury smart toilet options in Australia, bringing the kind of features once exclusive to high-end hotels and resorts into everyday bathrooms.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
